{"tid":2280612,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★突發！99間學校院舍爆上呼吸道感染涉逾千人","createTime":"2020-11-10T15:02:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-10T15:12:02.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"63a8af6d7d4e92c8693616378468ff185110cb8b","tid":2280612,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T15:02:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/5663276/org/2406845f5891346542d41bc733cfcb71.jpg/2q-Hys92MW2IxB1Zlu3RokOvaRjpadndrQWDLq0Fgy4?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F5663276%2Forg%2F2406845f5891346542d41bc733cfcb71.jpg%2F2q-Hys92MW2IxB1Zlu3RokOvaRjpadndrQWDLq0Fgy4%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=f0918e81&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n天氣轉涼，不少學校爆發上呼吸道感染。衞生防護中心今日（10日）再公布，有9間學校出現上呼吸道感染個案，共涉及一間幼兒中心、兩間幼稚園暨幼兒中心、四間幼稚園、CLEARWATER BAY SCHOOL（英基清水灣小學）及匡智元朗晨曦學校。9間學校共有295名學生不適，其中九龍塘又一村學校受感染學童人數最多，共涉及65人。自10月31日起至今日下午3時，共有99間學校及院舍爆發上呼吸道感染，共有1,066人中招。<br />\n<br />\n衞生防護中心會向這些爆發學童上呼吸道感染的學校，派發深喉唾液樣本瓶，為有關受影響班別的師生進行新冠病毒檢測，並建議有關班別停課不少於三日。中心強烈呼籲市民，以及院舍或學校員工提高警覺，時刻保持個人和環境衞生。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/547207/99%E9%96%93%E5%AD%B8%E6%A0%A1%E9%99%A2%E8%88%8D%E7%88%86%E4%B8%8A%E5%91%BC%E5%90%B8%E9%81%93%E6%84%9F%E6%9F%93%E6%B6%89%E9%80%BE%E5%8D%83%E4%BA%BA-%E8%8B%B1%E5%9F%BA%E6%B8%85%E6%B0%B4%E7%81%A3%E5%B0%8F%E5%AD%B833%E5%AD%B8%E7%AB%A5%E4%B8%AD%E6%8B%9B\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F547207%2F99%25E9%2596%2593%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E6%25A0%25A1%25E9%2599%25A2%25E8%2588%258D%25E7%2588%2586%25E4%25B8%258A%25E5%2591%25BC%25E5%2590%25B8%25E9%2581%2593%25E6%2584%259F%25E6%259F%2593%25E6%25B6%2589%25E9%2580%25BE%25E5%258D%2583%25E4%25BA%25BA-%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%259F%25BA%25E6%25B8%2585%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E7%2581%25A3%25E5%25B0%258F%25E5%25AD%25B833%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%25AB%25A5%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E6%25